{"tid":1587281,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"禮拜六 - 九龍區  足球Group","createTime":"2019-09-22T10:40:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-16T05:03:36.000Z","uid":103929,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ba688bf219b9aefd9e51c289b78c7d85584b61ce","tid":1587281,"uid":103929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T10:40:33.000Z","msg":"今次招人係搵一班固定斯文波腳<br />\n<br />\n要求<br />\n1.斯文，懂得收腳（唔係比賽唔使執著）<br />\n2.唔衝撞多手，唔亂撞人<br />\n3.有基本功，樂於組織，團隊精神，球品行先<br />\n（衛生波原因係個嗰要返工，避免受傷）<br />\n<br />\n一直選人試腳，踢走過大量獨食、球品差、脾氣差、潛水嘅人，寧缺毋濫。<br />\n<br />\n目前，群組連續2年每個星期六晚九龍區必踢<br />\n除非暴雨特發情況<br />\n群組內全部由陌生人開始認識、已經熟絡<br />\n現在均是固定波腳，人品球品甚佳<br />\n<br />\n年齡層：返工一族<br />\n<br />\n歡迎試腳，合資格才加wts gp<br />\ntelegram：<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/Relaxball\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FRelaxball&d=AaXh75k8ef15jyN5JBlvBkx5KyfgaA76LUEybGJClr4%3D&h=fd3118da\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/Relaxball</a>"},{"pid":"d5f4149530f14d52006ba4bd6b08155ea8f5bae6","tid":1587281,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T10:40:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"de8b7c4e3d6109201df3d351dc86ff9f1726359b","tid":1587281,"uid":32542,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T10:42:59.000Z","msg":"仲以為真係踢波"},{"pid":"a62610f2cc116644f4cbeb826bd235cab42568c8","tid":1587281,"uid":103929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de8b7c4e3d6109201df3d351dc86ff9f1726359b","tid":1587281,"uid":32542,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T10:42:59.000Z","msg":"仲以為真係踢波"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T11:32:34.000Z","msg":"？？？"},{"pid":"e1322d70b8e4f82dbd5307b18a8697f800f12694","tid":1587281,"uid":103929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T05:01:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/ass